### Buscar pedidos
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders?pageIndex=0
Cookie: authCookie={{auth_token}}
###

### Buscar detalhes de um pedido
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/1
Cookie: authCookie={{auth_token}}
# Altere o ID conforme necessário

